subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: NAPA Auto Parts will end its multimillion-dollar sponsorship of Michael Waltrip Racing at the end of the year, the latest fallout from the team’s effort to manipulate a race.
